---
interface Props {}

const {} = Astro.props;
---
<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
            <span class="bg-black text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full">What Is BlocFeed?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-roboto tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            BlocFeed – The Marketplace for Ideas
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 font-nunito text-gray-600">
           Great ideas are everywhere, but most never see the light of day. People lack funding, resources, or the right partners to make them real. BlocFeed changes that.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
        <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16">
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-black">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                             stroke="currentColor"
                             aria-hidden="true">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                  d="M12 16.5V9.75m0 0l3 3m-3-3l-3 3M6.75 19.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-1.41-8.775 5.25 5.25 0 0110.233-2.33 3 3 0 013.758 3.848A3.752 3.752 0 0118 19.5H6.75z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    Post Your Idea
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                    Create a detailed entry or a quick concept post. Add images, documents, or even a pitch video.
                </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-black">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                             stroke="currentColor"
                             aria-hidden="true">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                  d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    Protect Ownership
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                    Every idea is tied to a secure digital contract showing your share, rights, and terms of collaboration.
                </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-black">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
  <!-- Person 1 -->
  <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
  <!-- Person 2 -->
  <circle cx="16" cy="8" r="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
  <!-- Connection line -->
  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 16c1.5-2 4-3 7-3s5.5 1 7 3"/>
</svg>

                    </div>
                    Collaborate Seamlessly
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                    Use built-in text, voice, and video messaging to brainstorm, negotiate, and refine together.
                </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-black">
                       <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
     stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <!-- outer circle -->
  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
  
  <!-- dollar sign -->
  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 7v10" />
  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 9.5c0-1.1-1-2-3-2s-3 .9-3 2 .9 2 3 2 3 .9 3 2-.9 2-3 2-3-.9-3-2" />
</svg>

                    </div>
                    Profit Together
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Set equity splits, co-ownership, or royalty deals. Everyone’s role is respected and rewarded.
                </dd>
            </div>
        </dl>
    </div>
</div>